# Data Dictionary — liu2018_hotstreaks
Source: github.com/lu-liu/hotstreaks (Liu et al. 2018, Nature).
File: scientists_sample.txt — 1,000-scientist subsample of scientists_c10.txt (20,040 full).
Format: one career per line; works split by '|'; each work = raw_C10, rescaled_C10, year.
rescaled_C10 = per-work citation impact (higher = more impactful).
readme.txt describes the full dataset (artists/directors/scientists + citation.zip).
